gm-method: a missing .gm/exec-spool on first Skill(skill="gm") dispatch is normal unbootstrapped-repo state, never grounds to conclude gm is fictional/inapplicable. The remedy is identical to the dead-watcher case: bun x gm-plugkit@latest spool creates the tree, fetches wasm, starts serving. An agent that asserts infrastructure doesn't exist without running the one-command boot probe first has produced an unwitnessed claim -- the same anti-shape gm's own L3 witness discipline forbids everywhere else. SKILL.md now states this explicitly ahead of the Boot-before-dispatching section.